features
--------
- work with localstorage
  - parser
  - writer
  - autosave
  
- resetting needs to do more
  - scroll offsets
  - selection.clear()

- keyboard+drag to quickly add
  - rectangles

- UI
  - verb/cancel dialogs

- selection
  - multiselection

- zoom in/out

- undo!

- shapes
  - rectangle
  - horizontal rule
  - text label
  - text paragraph
  - various icons
  - icon and label
  - combobox
  - button
  - fancy arrows

- colour palette
  - black
  - white
  - 4 greys
  - blue
  - red
  - green
  - amber
  - orange

- text parsing e.g. this is *bold*
- saving
- loading
- selecting
- dragging
- resizing
- export to GIF

